lead_paragraph: England's players are reaping the benefits of being given a licence to thrill, said Jason Roy following the World Twenty20 semi-final victory by seven wickets against New Zealand on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Licence to Thrill Is Key for England, Says Roy
headline.main: Licence to Thrill Is Key for England, Says Roy
